## Distance Between Airports [/airport/distance/{airportCodeFrom}/{airportCodeTo}?user_key={user_key}&units={units}]

Get the distance between two airports. The API will return distance in either imperial or metric units.

+ Parameters

   + airportCodeFrom
   + airportCodeTo
   + user_key
   + units (optional)

### Get Distance [GET]

+ Response 200

   + Headers 

            Date: Wed, 13 Apr 2016 16:47:17 GMT
            Connection: keep-alive
            Content-Type: application/json

   + Body

            {
               "processingDurationMillis":868,
               "authorisedAPI":true,
               "success":true,
               "airline":null,
               "errorMessage":null,
               "distance":"8,208.6",
               "units":"km"
            }

